{
  "texts": [
    "Indeed, the first non-zero operator is dimension-8.",
    "It would be interesting to study this class of trispectra in more detail.",
    "JHEP05(2024)196 Example 2: spin-2 exchange in CCMWe now move to a second example where we consider the exchange of a spin-2 field with its dynamics described by the cosmological condensed matter physics scenario.",
    "In this case we take the bulk-bulk propagator to be parity-even κ = 0, and source the parity-violation via the interaction vertices.",
    "We therefore need one vertex to have an even number of spatial derivatives, and for the other to have an odd number."
  ]
}